00:08:37.752 --> 00:08:39.153 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TSUMUGI]
I can see everything.

00:08:39.387 --> 00:08:41.555 position:13% line:83% align:start
[SARASA] This is some next
level production design.

00:08:41.922 --> 00:08:43.290 position:38% line:83% align:start
[HIROTO]
Yeah, it's crazy.

00:08:51.065 --> 00:08:52.967 position:30% line:83% align:start
In Crossboard,
all the ASTRAL spaces

00:08:53.100 --> 00:08:55.102 position:24% line:83% align:start
