00:09:03.778 --> 00:09:05.646 position:35% line:83% align:start
Listen up,
'cause this bit's important.

00:09:06.247 --> 00:09:08.816 position:16% line:83% align:start
Crossboard is completely
integrated with ASTRAL.

00:09:09.050 --> 00:09:10.718 position:27% line:83% align:start
