00:10:42.409 --> 00:10:43.477 position:19% line:89% align:start
See the problem, here?

00:10:43.811 --> 00:10:45.012 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:45.412 --> 00:10:46.647 position:35% line:89% align:start
